{"tid":1330830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人人都係文宣 請善用Airdrop 大大力宣傳21/7金鐘見！","createTime":"2019-07-18T17:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T22:05:51.000Z","uid":69525,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5581b98b181480aa050ebdc72751f713cb02365b","tid":1330830,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"民賤聯用陰招想介走班接收資訊未必咁update既老年同中年人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以大家要大大力咁宣傳21/7先係對準五大訴求既遊行同野餐日子！<br />\n<br />\n淨係連登知唔夠 出面有好多人都未必清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以要做好文宣工作！<br />\n<br />\n想做文宣既你<br />\n除左整圖、落區派傳單、貼街招、連儂牆資訊站外<br />\n好好善用Airdrop功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先去 設定&gt;一般&gt;關於本機 改返個靚名<br />\n例子 就算人地唔接都可以透過你個名了解到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yawsYC0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyawsYC0.png&h=afbe6eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後去自己用Instagram簡單整張圖<br />\n又或者去文宣組拎圖(大把)<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFSggAmG8zrSjqjZRw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFSggAmG8zrSjqjZRw&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=2f26f3f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFSggAmG8zrSjqjZRw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=f5f31cb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkposter777</a><br />\n<br />\n然後用Airdrop send出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭地鐵既話 行足咁多卡會send到唔少<br />\n係地鐵站等人既話 又send<br />\n食飯放lunch 又send<br />\n唔嫌麻煩既話whatsapp send比朋友<br />\n最低限期 post ig story都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvaabZx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvaabZx.png&h=609c31aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CTzusxS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCTzusxS.png&h=106c0f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OtZusxT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOtZusxT.png&h=9b130765&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4tOH6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4tOH6d.png&h=d0ce91e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n集中21/7 重申20/7 係無任何遊行 旺角遊行已延期<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1326914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1326914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"650d821e226ca2bf0fddd314529e5877fe393bbf","tid":1330830,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"[7.21 遊行] 好撚重要 必需置頂!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327475</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定721去定唔去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">集中推呢幾個 熱門啲</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e08100270e7a741da93d4f0a9216859b3b564e20","tid":1330830,"uid":217844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uaF127V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuaF127V.png&h=162fe1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490abc07ff4ce6d142c693ea299e948ac7